text: This Gate 1 Sudden Valley home is ready for new owners! The level lot abuts to SVCA open space and is located in a terrific cul-de-sac with an amazing backyard that contains a huge deck for entertaining, playing, relaxing and the trees/shrubs give extra privacy. This 4 bedroom home has an attached 2-car garage, newer appliances (kitchen & laundry), instant-hot water, granite counters, kitchen bar, separate laundry, skylights, vaulted ceilings, and updated lighting throughout. The primary suite includes French door entrance, ceiling fan, en-suite bath with double sinks, jetted tub, and separate shower. The Sudden Valley community has a ton to offer with a pool, gym, beaches, marina, golf course, library, and trails.

Contemporary and eco-friendly, NEW Larrabee Springs Venture Townhomes feature, 8 panel solar system, 2 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, and modern design flooded with natural light. Explore the convenience of sidewalks and sustainable living with solar panels & EV wiring. Elevate the living experience with locally crafted cabinets by the renowned Highcraft Cabinets in Ferndale. Discover the perfect blend of style, functionality, and artisanal quality in these thoughtfully designed townhomes. Reservations Only. Prices subject to change. Showings available between 12-3pm, 7dys a week. Larrabee Springs Venture Townhomes

Relax the days away in your very own piece of heaven in The Glen at Maple Falls with this very well located recreational property. Backing up to green space and a trail to the Nooksack River, this private and well maintained 2012 park model with covered porch has all the amenities to make this your home away from home. The gazebo boasts a queen bed, while another bunkhouse provides two more sleeping spaces, perfect for friends. Shed space for extra storage rounds out this amazing property. Neighboring property is also for sale (MLS 2254695), partner with friends or buy both for added privacy, room for guests, and more. The Glen has 24/7 security, 2 pools (one year-round!), hot tub, clubhouses, sports courts and more!

Beautiful 2 bedroom 1-3/4 bath 1096 sq ft home located in the very desirable over 55 community known as Fieldstone Place. New roof, new carpet, new exterior paint, new SS appliance package & new insulated garage overhead door. Attached 2 car garage with sink. Vaulted ceilings. Walking distance to the community ctr, golf course, fitness club and fine dining. Short distance to downtown,

Step into your new sanctuary - a contemporary 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom manufactured home that embodies modern living. Nestled in a serene park setting, this property harmonizes comfort and style, creating an airy, welcoming ambiance from the moment you walk through the door. The spacious, well-lit living area seamlessly flows into the open kitchen, where stainless steel appliances, including a refrigerator, stove, dishwasher, and microwave, elevate both form and function. With its sleek design and abundant natural light, this kitchen is not just a culinary space but a statement of refined living. Additionally, the utility room offers convenient access to the back area through a rear door. Welcome to your new haven.

First time home buyer? Investor? Look no further! This two bed, two bath town house is centrally located in the heart of Bellingham just steps away from Rosevelt Park. This unit has great bones and an unbeatable proximity to schools, public transit, shopping & dining. Come see it for yourself!

Unlock the true potential of this early 1900s Craftsman, conveniently nestled in the heart of Sunnyland. Moments away from Trader Joes, restaurants, and more. This quaint residence is a blank canvas, awaiting the touch to make it yours. Home features a spacious living and dining area with tall ceilings. Both bedrooms are complete with en suite bathrooms, complemented by an additional full bath off the kitchen. Detached two-car garage features a finished 400-square-foot studio space, equipped with a kitchenette and full bathideal for guests, a home office, or potential rental income. If you've been waiting for the perfect opportunity to make your mark with sweat equity on a charming home in a desirable neighborhood, this is the one!

Just 1 BLOCK from WWU's beautiful campus & with MILLION DOLLAR VIEWS of the Bay, Islands & City! This 2-spacious-bedroom 1-full-bath condo is a perfect alternative to renting or dorm living. All-electric, easy to own & maintain, 7 steps up from sidewalk-level & ideally located. Enjoy home-cooked meals in the open kitchen then take it out to the view balcony for Bellingham Bay's World Class Sunsets! Features in-unit laundry w/washer/dryer included. Designated off-street parking spot + street parking. Seconds to WWU, minutes to downtown, affordable investment w/no rental cap! Take advantage of Bellingham's appreciating property values then sell when you're done! Wealth-building-and-preservation 101 at 729 High St. #203.

Welcome home to Glenhaven! This charming property offers 3 beds, 3 baths, and 2004 sq ft of comfortable living space. The great room downstairs is perfect for entertaining or unwinding after a long day. Enjoy the convenience of walking trails and the weekly visit of a mobile book bus every Monday. This desirable neighborhood offers a community pool, access to the lakes, parks and more. This home is a true gem!

This gorgeous straw bale home has a unique beauty & feel with its soft curves, 10' wood & beam ceilings, deep window wells & R-48 insulating factor. Walk into its warm, organic style that wraps you in a feeling of peace and tranquility. Special features include a beach rock fireplace, guest wing w/ private bath, a 2nd floor bonus room (plus art closet), lovely gardens & a studio above the 2 car garage. Nice indoor-outdoor flow with Fr. doors leading to private, covered deck. This lovely home is in a fantastic location, just a short walk to the beach, easy walk to the library, store and post office. Here is a great opportunity for those that work from home, artists or those that want a shared or multi-generational layout.
nearby_schools: Lummi Elementary School, Ferndale School District, Lummi High School

text: Endless potential! This home resides in the coveted Edgemoor neighborhood, only minutes from Historic Fairhaven. Three bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, lightly lived in, and personality throughout! Solarium adds that mid-century character that has made a comeback in recent decor. Daylight basement never been finished, ready for your ideas... family room? MIL suite? you name it! Outside entrance makes for unlimited options. Mature landscaping, including Rhododendrons and privacy trees around property - a little hedge trimming and weeding will make this property shine and some elbow grease will give you immediate equity. Don't miss out!

Welcome to Crossridge Urban Community! Brand new single family homes that have been thoughtfully designed with architectural & community integrity, each home feels custom with its elevated finishes and interior design. The Padden model has all the living on main floor that extends out through modern French doors onto a large covered patio. Private backyard with 6' fence, gate, modern pavers, low maintenance turf and raised bed planters and a corner lot. Upstairs you'll find the primary with attached ensuite and 2 more bedrooms with connected bath. Don't forget the detached flex space with half bath and separate entrance that can be used as an office, family room, or for guests.

This architecturally designed and custom built Whistler-style NW craftsman home is very unique and privately situated on over 10 acres (2 parcel #'s), surrounded by evergreens overlooking a pond and a stream. The details of this home are incredible with main floor living, wood timbers and beams, dramatic entry, open floor plan, generously sized rooms, wood-lined vaulted ceilings, floor-to-ceiling south facing windows for passive solar heating, wrap-around deck with covered outdoor kitchen, new high-efficiency furnace and heat pump, new on-demand hot water tank, mini kitchen set up for an ADU in the basement, and a 40 x 48 shop with covered wood storage. This estate is located just 15 minutes from Bellingham and it is so tranquil and serene.

Live in this stunning waterfront home with views of BOTH Drayton Harbor and the ocean (includes Mt. Baker and SE to SW panoramic unobstructed - one of only two sites!). Private gated entry with direct access to miles of trails and beaches. This unit also has a huge patio and landscaped yard (over 11, 000 sq ft total). The attention to detail, soaring ceilings and high-end finishes make this unit arguably one of the best. Butler pantry off kitchen, wine fridge, high-end appliances throughout, also has a bonus living space with stunning views above the garage - do not miss any details - call for a private tour!

Excellent opportunity to purchase a vacant lot close to town, with views of the Bay and mountains AND ability to proceed with a home construction with septic and building permits already completed. The owners of this property have spent over 2 years with all the technical data required with the county in getting the home ready to start construction and their immediate plans then changed and they are unable to proceed. Thus, the septic permit has been approved and all of the building plans for a home have been approved by the county and now all needed is to take over and start. The construction company has indicated they still can get this project scheduled in immediately to break ground if you wanted to still us them (but not required).

Charming turn of the century craftsman home located in the heart of Lynden within walking distance to schools, shopping, dining and bus lines! Bring your ideas and vision to this home with tons of potential. 3 beds upstairs and 2 down for a total of 5 beds & 1 bath w/ extra office or living/flex space on the main level. Potentially add a bathroom and convert this space to a main level primary bedroom in a remodel. Solid wood floors have the potential of being refinished to bring the original beauty back. A good opportunity to move in now and renovate over time for equity building in a great Lynden location. Vacant, view anytime.

Come see this spectacular Lake Whatcom view lot with the incredible building site already cleared. No guesswork on this lot of what your view will be. Build your dream home on this incredible lot that gets all day sun. Owner has approved plans available or design your own dream home. You can see Stewart Mt, Galbraith Mt, and Sudden Valley from this site. You feel like you are miles away from civilization but you're only 10 mins to Barkley Village. Keep the world close with fiber optics. Enjoy the community walking trail around the project while the gated access gives peace of mind. The abundant wildlife gives the nature lover constant viewing possibilities. Don't miss the opportunity to see this estate property.

A classic Stephen Fuller-designed Colonial Revival home situated on a gated 5-acre estate. A wandering, tree-lined driveway leads to a stunning residence set back approx 700 from the road for additional privacy. This 6-bedroom home showcases timeless design, finishes, millwork, refined crown molding, and a chef's kitchen. The covered front and back porches are cozy gathering spaces with captivating territorial views. The pergola-framed stone patio with built-in grill, sink, outdoor fireplace and new 7-person hot tub makes for an ideal location to entertain. The property has a 4-stage whole house reverse osmosis water system, full high-speed Wi-Fi mesh coverage, and is located 10 minutes from the US/Canada border crossing.

Beautiful treed lot backing up to hundreds of acres of protected hillside forest. Just West of Galbraith Mountain biking trails. Currently no access or services to the lot, which would make a great holding investment for the future. Buy now and benefit later when this lot is buildable for your forested lot close to world-class mountain biking.

Discover your dream home in desirable Edgemoor neighborhood! This stunning single-level home was fully updated in 2012 & has been meticulously maintained since. Home boasts beautiful kitchen w/ elegant cherry wood cabinets & kitchen island, perfect for entertaining. The home features oak hardwood & slate floors, complemented by cozy gas fireplace w/ slate surround. Enjoy year-round comfort in the Four Seasons sunroom, w/ heated slate floor, providing a serene space to relax. The house is equipped w/ A/C & generator, ensuring comfort & convenience year round. Enjoy time on the spacious front deck or on the patio in the fenced backyard, ideal for outdoor gatherings. Property includes a custom-designed garden shed & tons of gardening space!

Introducing The Alder B plan, with 2 car garage on the southwest perimeter of Woodberry's new gated community at Semiahmoo. This plan lives like a one-level home and has 2 bedrooms with office on the main floor including the Primary suite. There are 1.75 baths on the Primary Level. Up you have 2 bedrooms, full bath and loft area. Quality flooring, heat pumps with heating, and air conditioning. Soft close cabinets, quartz countertops, nice lighting package, island in the kitchen. Heated floors in the Primary and so much more. Come see the model home now open. Area amenities, Golf Marina, Tennis club, Ornithologist dream, walking trails kayaking, biking. Sage Homes Northwest Site Registration No. 4908.

South-West facing building lot in South Beach less than a 5-minute walk to the warm sands and tidelands of the most sought-after beach area in Point Roberts where swimming, skim boarding, building sandcastles or just plain relaxing in the sun can consume your day. Point Roberts Marina is only a 10-minute walk away. This lot comes with undivided 1/250 interest in Beach Reserve is cleared, level and ready to build on - sunshine all day long. Good potential for ocean view from a second story. Expired Septic Design shows that this lot has great soils. Be sure to check link to online Video!

Brand new 2-story home which has just been completed in the lakeside & golf course community of Sudden Valley. this 2-story, 3 bedroom home is located on a flat, corner lot, which is surrounded by 2 vacant lots which have been turned into permanent green-belt by the Sudden Valley community. Lots of 'elbow room' here! Enjoy an open great room with kitchen, dining area & living room on the main level. Easy access to a large, low level deck directly off of the living area. The kitchen has white cabinet package, large island with quartz counter top, & stainless steel appliances. The primary bedroom is upstairs & has ensuite bath with large glass enclosed shower & walk-in closet. Room for a small office upstairs as well - or sitting area.

This is it - the dream home right next to Lake Padden! This charming 1940s Dutch Colonial home has it all: location, style & charm. Main floor is warm & welcoming: a fantastic classic floor plan with 2 delightful main living areas each with a welcoming wood stove. The recently updated kitchen is bright & beautiful complimenting the character of the home. Upstairs features 2 bedrooms overlooking the beautiful yard & a full bathroom. Life outside is a delight: natural landscaping, private patio w/ fire pit, hot tub, fenced yard & mature trees. Have it all with quiet neighborhood living & daily walks, runs or paddles at Lake Padden park. World class mountain biking at Galbraith, parks and beaches just minutes away. Must see this one in person!

Located just outside of the city limits, this home in Woodbine Estates is ready for you. New roof last year, new exterior paint, new windows in bedrooms, new carpet in bedrooms, new furnace in '18. The flow between the living area, kitchen, and dining room is spacious. Lots of cabinet space in the kitchen. The new KitchenAid stove in the center island is a bonus! All appliances stay including the freezer in the garage. Large front yard and in the back, enjoy the park like setting with plenty of privacy on the back deck. Open the gate in the back yard for access to the trail system. Bike to Lake Padden, Whatcom Falls Park, or Galbraith! Plenty of room to park RV on side of driveway. Located close to town for convenience! Come see this gem!

Discover serenity in this charming 3 bed, 1 bath Alabama Hill home on a large sunny lot. Updated with a newer roof, gutters, and vinyl windows for efficiency and comfort. Ductless Mini split for economical heating and cooling. Enormous fully fenced backyard includes a concrete patio, apple and plum trees, blueberry bushes and planter boxes. Large driveway + tons of off-street parking. Steps away from St. Claire Park and the Whatcom Falls Park trailhead, and minutes to all the amenities Bellingham has to offer.

Private & peaceful retreat on large double lot above Emerald Lake. Large sunny deck, wraps around 3 sides of the home for outside entertaining! Vaulted interior w/ floor to ceiling windows provides a light filled home. Newer energy efficient wood fireplace. Spacious loft creates extra living space. Nicely finished daylight basement w/ spacious great room, Bdrm, shop, office & bath. Also is plumbed/wired for 2nd kitchen. Relax on private back deck & live in comfort & tranquil privacy near the Lake. Only 7 miles to downtown Bellingham/10 minutes to Barkley Village. Located on a secluded 1.3 acre lot w/nearby boat launch. Walk to private waterfront access as well as walking trails. Sought after large, semi-level, useable front yard!

Indulge in the awe-inspiring, unobstructed views of the Bay and Islands from this exquisite residence. Impeccably designed home offers an unparalleled sense of refined luxury and comfort. The living room seamlessly flows onto a spacious deck, where the panoramic vistas become an extension of your living space, perfect for entertaining or unwinding. Well-appointed kitchen is a culinary delight. Primary, a spa-like ensuite offers a peaceful escape. Generously scaled rooms provide ample space for relaxation and productivity, while the library is a retreat for literary escapes. Meticulously landscaped grounds, access to outdoor recreation and in proximity to urban conveniences, this home epitomizes a blend of upscale living and natural beauty.

Outstanding opportunity for multi-generational living at this delightful sought after Bob Hall Road location...2, 070 sq ft 3 bedroom/2 bathroom main house + second stand alone building with 750 sq ft guest quarters. The main house features a light & bright open concept kitchen/living/dining design with updated quartz counters & LVP flooring. The versatile outbuilding has ADU potential with 1 bedroom/1 bathroom, full kitchen, living room + 2 car attached garage. Don't miss the incredible sunrise and sunsets or the covered outdoor relaxing/entertaining area. This 1.2 acre mountain view estate is ideal for the buyer looking for privacy or for loads of space for boat/RV parking. Bonus: Lynden School District + Xfinity is available here!

Welcome to your dream home in the heart of the popular east side of Lynden! This stunning 2, 029 square foot, 2-story residence offers 3 bedrooms, a den w/elegant French doors, & 2.5 baths. The property boasts a 7, 405 square foot lot, featuring a fully fenced backyard complete with extended patio & charming gazebo, ideal for outdoor gatherings. The garden shed provides additional storage for your gardening tools. Vaulted ceilings in the gathering room create an open airy feel, along with a cozy gas fireplace. The kitchen is outfitted with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, & bar seating. Enjoy the convenience of a spacious main floor primary bedroom, providing a serene retreat with easy access. Dont miss this opportunity!

This sale includes, 2 parcels, totaling just under 40 acres. Located East off Historic Hwy SR 9. Raw land, off grid home site, tucked away amongst nature, just below the foothills of the Twin Sisters. Black Slough running thru, provides a retreat for a variety of wildlife and natural vegetation. Access does require working with County.

Fantastic starter, rental VRBO or getaway. Located walking distance from Birch Bay State Park and endless trails and beaches nearby. This home has been completely refinished. New windows, trim, flooring, appliances, beautiful walk in shower in the primary suite, paint, mini-split for air and list goes on and on. Large fenced yard with a patio and 2 storage sheds. The kitchen features all new cabinetry and solid countertops. You will not find a home with all the features this boasts for an affordable price like this!

This is the perfect lake house sited in the most serene and quiet part of Lake Samish. The 3 bed 2 bath home spans a comfortable 1846 sf on a generous 1/4 ac lot. Inside enjoy beautiful views, a cozy fireplace, and skylights that filter abundant natural light throughout the space. The kitchen boasts modern appliances and a large open layout, perfect for entertaining. Outside, the private dock and elevated deck provide opportunity to experience lake life at its best. Host guests on the deck while taking in the stunning scenery. There is parking for a boat/RV on the property. With its unbeatable location and desirable features, this home is the epitome of lakeside living. Truly a very unique opportunity to own on coveted Lake Samish.

Country living right in town. This updated classic craftsman home offers full width front porch. Expansive upstairs primary bedroom with sitting space, office area, built in shelves and ample storage. Original fir floors in living room, stainless appliances in kitchen. New paint, ductless split system & water heater. Recent repairs to basement completed and now ready for the personal finishes. Private backyard deck leads to secure concrete block outbuilding for the hobbyist, large sun filled garden space and fruit trees, berry bushes and fenced yard sloping down to Squalicum Creek. Great place to get away and still bike to your favorite Friday night spot. 1st time on market since built in 1925.

Discover coastal living in this charming one-level home on a corner lot, just a block from Birch Bay Beach. Enjoy private beach access with beach rights! This 3-bedroom, 2-bath gem offers vaulted ceilings, an open floor plan, and updated kitchen with marble countertops and ample storage. The east-facing front ensures you wake up to beautiful morning sun. The heart of the home opens to a fully fenced backyard, filled with a variety of plants, flowers and plenty of garden space. Just 15 minutes to Canada and 90 minutes to Seattle, this home is perfectly located for both relaxation and adventure. Your seaside retreat awaits!

A Fantastic investment opportunity awaits with this well maintained fourplex in Lynden. Spacious units with natural light throughout. Units A and D are single level units. Units B and C are two story units with rooms upstairs and generous living space downstairs. Unit A has a large side yard, all units have back deck and yard space. Conveniently located. Beautiful landscaping separates the two sides of the 4-plex in the front. Newer roof! Methodically built to minimize nasal inhalation of cow excretion. Located at the end of cul de sac with fast access to E Badger Rd.

Amazing Home with Buyer Bonus for fighting the terrible rates, this forever home is Nestled in serene PNW forest on a 4.57-acre property, minutes from town, this newly constructed modern home boasts an impressive 3090 sqft of contemporary living space. Expansive windows throughout the home frame picturesque views of the lush forest. The open-concept living area features vaulted ceilings, white oak engineered h/wd floors, and a stunning double sided fireplace. Gourmet kitchen, where top of the line appliances, waterfall edge island, and a large walk in pantry create an ideal environment for culinary creativity. Two laundry rooms provide added convenience. 3 bedrooms and an extra finished room/nursery/gym upstairs. Buy with confidence!

Opportunity awaits in the coveted Cornwall Park neighborhood! Newer roof (2017), detached oversized 1-car garage & an easy layout; all it needs is your vision and finishing touches to shine again. The original hardwood floors & wood burning fireplace create a nostalgic charm while the large kitchen make it practical for modern day living. Beautiful fully-fenced yard with room to play or start a garden. Large patio, great for entertaining & enjoying warm summer nights. Situated in the heart of the neighborhood with easy access to groceries, breweries, schools, waterfront, city parks, public transportation & more! Plan to live car-free in this highly walkable neighborhood? Turn the oversized 1-car garage into a detached ADU (Buyer to verify).

20 gorgeous acres complete with a classic Northwest Craftsman Home alongside a stream and surrounded by towering evergreens. Located amidst a plethora of outside entertainment...skiing, horseback, hiking, climbing, hunting & fishing, Silver Lake & mountain biking too. Every room has a view. The Kitchen & dining room share a fireplace & the woodstove keeps the living room cozy. Upstairs is freshly remodeled. Lots of extra space downstairs. Lifetime roof. Lodge Style entry. Huge Shop for 7 cars. Private acreage combines massive conifers w/a 9-hole golf course, close to miles of state and federal land to recreate in! Horses, weddings, hiking, vacation rental & Golf of course...or all of it. Location, location, location!

Wake up to beautiful sunrises over the Bay & Mt Baker, revel in the glow of a sunset on the mountain. Waterfront patio for your crab feast; launch your kayak or SUP from your own backyard! Youll love the peaceful serenity of Sandy Point Shores! Inside youll appreciate the wall of windows to bring in the million dollar views. Nicely updated kitchen, waterfront dining, cozy fireplace. Upstairs youll find a large Primary Suite. 2 bdrms / full bath on the main, + laundry. 2 car garage, side yard could park an RV/boat. Newer metal roof, freshly painted inside/out, new high-end waterproof laminate floors. SP amenities: Marina, Golf, Tennis, Clubhouse. Come see this beautiful home & wonderful community on the water. Start living your dream!

Step inside this well maintained Chuckanut Crest home to discover a panorama of views of the San Juan Islands, Chuckanut Bay, and Salish Sea from almost every room. Gated community with tennis courts, and walking and biking trails close by. Natural light from southwest exposure floods into the expansive living spaces and gallery of windows facing Dot Island. Gourmet kitchen with great room and large deck to enjoy year round entertaining. The breathtaking scenery includes colorful sunsets, wildlife & sea life. Spacious Primary bedroom w/ lovely ensuite offer a serene setting, away from it all. A large array of possibilities for any lifestyle as the home has unique spaces separate from each other for space assignment for work, play & hobbies.

Completely renovated one-level Geneva neighborhood home, on an oversized private, tranquil lot in a quiet cul-de-sac is here! The open floor plan with vaulted ceilings and skylights greet you with a tastefully renovated kitchen and island, new bathrooms with walk-in showers, new flooring, interior and exterior paint, custom lighting throughout, new heat pump and furnace, new water heater, new decking and fenced yard. A perfect rec/play room for entertaining off the oversized two-car garage. The babbling creek behind the house will help you relax, and enjoy the low-maintenance NW yard and landscaping. All this and more just steps from world-famous Galbraith mountain trails, up the hill from Lake Whatcom, Whatcom Falls and minutes to town.

This charming 1898 Victorian house beautifully marries its timeless appeal with modern upgrades, offering the perfect blend of historic character and modern comforts. The recently remodeled bathroom offers the luxury of in-floor heating, warming your feet as you start your day. The heart of the home boasts modern touches like stainless steel appliances that are a few years old, making every culinary adventure a joy. In 2020, the house received a fresh coat of paint, enhancing its classic beauty. Outside, the newly installed front porch and yard invites you to relax and soak in the vibrant neighborhood atmosphere. Nestled in one of Bellingham's most sought after neighborhoods everything you need is just a stroll away.

Great opportunity to own a light and bright condo just steps to Western Washington University! This top floor unit has been lovingly refreshed and is move-in ready with new quartz counters, stainless steel appliances, fresh paint and pergo flooring. Enjoy easy access with no stairs to the entrance and take in the beautiful sunsets with west facing views over the bay and downtown. Possibility to live in or a potential investment opportunity in a wonderful location.

Huge price reduction! Come see this great home on 5 lots. Tax assessment at $836, 000. This property is perfect for vacationing, living and enjoying time on the lake. Come enjoy all that Glenhaven has to offer - seasonal pool, tennis court, clubhouse and 2 lakes for fishing and boating. All contents of house included with the sale, except for wooden boat and some personal tools.

Charming Southside of Bellingham top floor end unit in the sought after Cypress Condo Complex. Enjoy the abundant light, spacious kitchen, and ample full bathroom with in unit stackable washer and dryer. Step out onto the patio and enjoy the evening breeze as you take in the South Hills and Chuckanut Mountain. Additional storage unit just a few steps from the door. Additional amenities include secure building, elevator, gated entry, fitness center and outdoor covered bike storage. Easy walk or bike ride to Joe's Garden, REI, groceries, shopping, dining, and local trails.

This fully remodeled home offers the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. Nestled in a serene location with a picturesque stream nearby, it feels like a world away, yet it's just a five-minute drive to Whole Foods and quick access to I-5. Enjoy a short walk to the beautiful Whatcom Falls Park and Lafeen's, or take a quick bike ride to Galbraith Mountain and Lake Whatcom. Inside and out, everything is new, featuring modern amenities such as a mini-split system for efficient heating and cooling. The spacious layout includes a huge primary bedroom, two additional bedrooms, and two full bathrooms. The home is also equipped with all new appliances, making it move-in ready. Don't miss this unique opportunity to call it your own!

Behold, newly adorned with modern grace, manufactured home, nestled in the esteemed Sandy Point Heights. Corner lot is over 1/3 acre, in cul-de-sac, this haven boasts a secluded yard, ample garden space, & sundry outbuildings including a 20x30 shop. With 1, 296 sq ft, the abode offers all necessities on one level, with three chambers for sleep and two for cleansing, a grand living space, skylights, & a fridge & range of stainless gleam. Recent enhancements include LVP flooring, paint, countertops, & fixtures. The capacious shop w/dog run brims with potential. Relish summer's eve beside a private fire pit or covered pergola. Sandy Point Heights offers a 9-hole golf course, community pool, club house, playground, boat launch and beach access.

Sweet Craftsman Home in a prime location in the Columbia Neighborhood. This solid, well cared for home has a beautiful yard and is surrounded by lovely character homes and great neighbors. Off street alley parking along with a one car garage. New 220 power to garage. Two nicely sized bedrooms upstairs and one smaller bedroom on the main level. Just steps to Carl Lobe Park and 2 blocks to Elizabeth Park. Your chance to live in this cherished neighborhood!

Clean and affordable home on fully fenced lot! Where to start on this exceptional property. First, you get a spacious 924 square feet 2 bedroom home, with fresh interior paint, newer flooring, remodeled bathroom, new hot water heater, all new plumbing and a free standing woodstove for a great second heat source. Second, we head outside and find a fully fenced 6 foot chain link fence with separate garden area and separate dog area! Plant a beautiful garden and don't worry about critters getting in there and eating all your hard work! Huge covered deck brings you outdoors in any kind of weather. Wait, we haven't talked about the wood shed and 2 other large sheds with enough storage for anyone! All this is for $199, 000?! Yep! Ready, set, go!

Welcome to 3110 Bennett Dr, where modern comforts meet country charm in the heart of Bellingham. This beautifully renovated home, nestled on nearly an acre of fully fenced, level land, features vibrant fruit trees, flower gardens, and a cozy fire pit. Extensive updates include new bathrooms, wiring, appliances, windows and more, you can move in and start making memories right away. Inside, enjoy a country kitchen with a spacious pantry and a laundry. The large driveway and substantial gate to the backyard provide ample space for boats, RVs, and more. A fabulous shop/creative space with a wood stove awaits your projects and hobbies. Just blocks from Little Squalicum Beach, this home offers the perfect blend of seclusion and accessibility.

Comfort meets convenience in this newly updated 3-bed, 2-bath home. Hidden in the picturesque Birch Bay Village, this gem offers 1, 404 SF of living space. Built in 2005, it boasts vaulted ceilings, a skylight, a luxurious walk-in closet, and an expansive primary bathroom. Stay cozy during winter with new ductless mini-splits for energy-efficient heating and cooling, charming wood stove, fiber-optic internet. Recent upgrades include 30-year roof, freshly painted exterior, state-of-the-art gutters with leaf guards, wired generator, landscape refresh, and new flooring throughout. Don't miss the generously sized detached garage/shop. As a resident of BBV, you have exclusive access to private marinas/boat launches, a golf course, parks & pools!

Soak up Mount Baker views from every corner of this tranquil, flat 4.7-acre property! Fantastic north Bellingham location with a single-level home and all the outbuildings you could desire. The one-owner home has fresh interior and exterior paint, newer roof and hot water heater, brand new kitchen appliances, new laminate flooring, and refinished decks. Spacious floorplan is set up to easily convert to 3 bedrooms. Enjoy mountain views and morning sunshine from the expansive front deck, and sunsets from the back deck and level yard. 2-bay shop plus a pole building, both with metal roofs, provide endless options for your creativity/hobby farm. Direct access to Mount Baker Hwy, I5, and Bellingham amenities. Don't miss this opportunity!

Welcome to 3108 Crestline Drive, a mid-century modern gem nestled on a tranquil dead end street and perfectly positioned to the trail system. This lovingly maintained home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a generous open layout featuring beautiful terracotta tile and maple hardwood floors. Step outside onto the sprawling deck and savor the tranquility, ideal for hosting gatherings during the warmer months. Delight in the professionally manicured English garden and charming tea house, offering a serene escape in the backyard. The cedar shed offers ample space for all of your outdoor projects or a beautiful studio space for your new hobbies. Embrace the chance to call this modern sanctuary your own.
